96
00:11:12,041 --> 00:11:13,547
Nádherne voniaš.

97
00:11:17,797 --> 00:11:20,108
Ste v poriadku?

98
00:11:20,108 --> 00:11:21,672
Cítim sa omnoho lepšie.

99
00:11:23,329 --> 00:11:25,170
Ďakujem.

100
